      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING WITNESS (2) shapes well for this on his swift win a few runs back, getting around this track over 622m in 35.59 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Rates on top and can find winning form again. RAYMAR SHAME (4) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (29.70) at Gosford in a Grade 4/5 over 515m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Sure to measure up. GRETA (8) doesn't show much early dash but winds into her races, two back missing the frame but last time hitting the line hard to place when third (29.77) in a Grade 4/5 at The Gardens last time. Strike rate this course strong having won four of seven tries. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Winning chance. LAYLA'S LILLY (1) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this trip.",
